repository-code: "https://github.com/danielkremen818/prompt-optimizer"
url: "https://github.com/danielkremen818/prompt-optimizer#readme"
abstract: >-
  A Claude Code slash command (/p) that rewrites a request into an optimized,
  reasoning-maximizing prompt — applying structured context, specificity,
  meta-instructions for extended thinking, and skip-comments that preserve quoted
  text — then immediately carries the optimized prompt out.
keywords:
  - claude-code
  - claude-code-plugin
  - prompt-engineering
  - meta-prompting
  - extended-thinking
